        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/f07891/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T19:25:10.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Anyone had this recently, any advice on how long to decant?</p>\n<p>Back story: My little brother just got engaged. I want to take him out for steak. I found a pristine bottle of '95 Haut Brion at below-market price. Little bro likes the good stuff, but doesn\u2019t usually buy at that price point (I only rarely buy at this price point), and I want to treat him to a nicer Bordeaux than he\u2019s probably ever had.</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance. Appreciate you all.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 11,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-04T05:51:58.762Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
