      {
        "id": 3192577,
        "name": "Gary Rust",
        "username": "Gary_Rust",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/b5e925/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T21:04:53.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have one bottle of the 1995 Haut Brion and haven\u2019t tried it, but I have had the 1998 Haut Brion and gave it a 3 hour decant.  The '98 was open with a complex nose and lots of bright fruit, but still young and a bit puckery.</p>",
