        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jay_miller/{size}/832_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T22:00:30.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Haven\u2019t had this but based on other 95s I was going to suggest a <em>minimum</em> 2 hour decant. I\u2019m not surprised to hear that 3 is better.</p>",
