      {
        "id": 3192600,
        "name": "Justin Goodman",
        "username": "HoosJustinG",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/h/b5ac83/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-05T22:09:10.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>While 95 is not the 89, I\u2019d be careful about buying something like H-B at a screaming deal price. This is not a niche bottle that would be difficult to move or a bottle that needs the \u201cright\u201d collector to come along. It has pretty predictable value, and H-B will always be H-B \u2026 especially a \u201cpristine\u201d bottle.</p>\n<p>Your brother\u2019s engagement is a special occasion, and you\u2019re thoughtful for treating him to such a fantastic bottle of wine. Just a quick word of caution before jumping in with two feet or getting tunnel vision on a single bottle. I\u2019d only buy such a bottle from a trusted source no matter the price.</p>",
