        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/d_zurcher/{size}/768_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-07-06T11:58:02.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"8\" data-topic=\"171844\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I\u2019m hoping the OP got the answers\u2026 thread drift slightly\u2026  Decant time for a 1998?  similar 2-3 hours?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Took a '98 to a restaurant days before the pandemic shutdown last year. Opened about 2 hours before dinner, decanted, rinsed out the bottle, and poured back in. It was in a really good place for the entire dinner.</p>",
